        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42068691/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42068691/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55598879/" class=" " title="流行的">流行的</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="42068691">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">理想国译丛序
……我们希望保持一种非功利的兴趣：对世界的丰富性、复杂性本身充满兴趣，真诚的渴望理解他人的经验。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-03-03 21:07</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                理想国译丛序<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>……我们希望保持一种非功利的兴趣：对世界的丰富性、复杂性本身充满兴趣，真诚的渴望理解他人的经验。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
